headline: iCRYO Named for Third Time to Inc. 5000 List of Fastest-Growing Private Companies in America
summary: iCRYO, a leading provider of health, wellness, and longevity services, is honored to announce its inclusion on the prestigious 2025 Inc. 5000 list, which ranks the fastest-growing private companies in the United States. This recognition serves as a bellwether of the brand's consistent growth, highlighting the viability of its franchise and medical business models and its unwavering commitment to improving lives through affordable wellness care.
